To build LExAu

* Make sure you have installed the GHC Haskell compiler
* Install version 2 of the alex parser generator:
  $ cabal install 'alex<3'
* copy file 'config.mk.example' to 'config.mk' and adapt it to your system if necessary
* run 'make'

To run the LExAu tests run the command 'lexau' in directory 'dist/build/lexau'.
